          Singapore's growth-focused marketing agency. We transform your drafts into reality, 
          elevating growth for your business.
        </p>
        <div class="flex gap-3">
          <a href="https://www.linkedin.com/company/jraftcreative" target="_blank" class="w-9 h-9 bg-dark-700 text-dark-300 rounded-lg flex items-center justify-center hover:bg-primary-500 hover:text-white transition-all duration-300">
